OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FPrison job advert banned   
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Ffor racial stereotyping    
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, A prison job advert showing a black    
OL,6, inmate and a white officer has been    
OL,7, banned due to racial stereotyping.     
OL,9,FThe Ministry of Justice's (MoJ)        
OL,10,Fpaid-for Facebook ad showed "an        
OL,11,Fimbalanced power dynamic", the         
OL,12,FAdvertising Standards Authority (ASA)  
OL,13,Fhas ruled.                             
OL,15,FThis reinforced a negative stereotype  
OL,16,Fbased on the association between black 
OL,17,Fmen and criminal activity, it said.    
OL,19,FThe MoJ had argued the campaign showed 
OL,20,Fphotos of real officers and prisoners, 
OL,21,Fand the type of engagement they have.  
